<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DEMAN.SOTRE</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/assets/deman.png?v=9">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/favicon.ico?v=5">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css?v=6">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="page-bg" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="page-bg__gradient"></div>
        <div class="page-bg__orb page-bg__orb--1"></div>
        <div class="page-bg__orb page-bg__orb--2"></div>
        <div class="page-bg__orb page-bg__orb--3"></div>
        <div class="page-bg__grid"></div>
        <div class="page-bg__slashes page-bg__slashes--left" aria-hidden="true">/////</div>
        <div class="page-bg__slashes page-bg__slashes--right" aria-hidden="true">/////</div>
    </div>

    <div id="keyauthOverlay" class="token-overlay hidden" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="keyauthOverlayTitle">
        <div class="token-scene">
            <div class="token-scene__glow"></div>
            <div class="token-card">
                <div class="token-card__brand-visual">
                    <img class="token-card__cls-logo" src="/assets/deman.png?v=9" width="96" height="96" alt="DEMAN.SOTRE" decoding="async" />
                </div>
                <div class="token-card__brand token-card__brand--cls">DEMAN.SOTRE</div>
                <p class="token-card__subtitle">License verification</p>
                <h2 class="token-card__title" id="keyauthOverlayTitle">Enter license key</h2>
                <p class="token-card__hint">Paste your KeyAuth license key. <a id="keyauthPanelLink" href="https://keyauth.cc/app/?page=licenses" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Manage licenses</a></p>
                <label class="token-field">
                    <span class="token-field__label">License key</span>
                    <div class="token-field__box">
                        <span class="token-field__icon token-field__icon--green" aria-hidden="true">◆</span>
                        <input type="text" id="keyauthInput" class="token-field__input" placeholder="Paste license key…" autocomplete="off" spellcheck="false" />
                    </div>
                </label>
                <button type="button" id="keyauthSaveBtn" class="token-card__submit">
                    <span>Continue</span>
                    <span class="token-card__submit-shine" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                </button>
                <div id="keyauthError" class="token-card__error" role="alert"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="tokenOverlay" class="token-overlay hidden">
        <div class="token-scene">
            <div class="token-scene__glow"></div>
            <div class="token-card">
                <button type="button" id="tokenOverlayDismiss" class="token-overlay-dismiss" aria-label="Dismiss — open app without token">✕</button>
                <div class="token-card__brand-visual">
                    <img class="token-card__cls-logo" src="/assets/deman.png?v=9" width="120" height="120" alt="DEMAN.SOTRE" decoding="async" />
                </div>
                <div class="token-card__brand token-card__brand--cls">DEMAN.SOTRE</div>
                <p class="token-card__subtitle">Secure access to your inventory</p>
                <h2 class="token-card__title">Sign in with platform</h2>
                <p class="token-card__hint">Paste your game token (Bearer prefix supported). It is stored locally on this device after verification.</p>
                <p class="auth-platform-heading">Sign in with platform</p>
                <div class="auth-platform-grid" id="tokenAuthPlatformGrid" role="group" aria-label="Choose login platform">
                    <button type="button" class="auth-platform-btn auth-platform-btn--steam" data-provider="steam" title="Steam — browser login">
                        <span class="auth-platform-btn__ico"><img class="auth-platform-btn__ico-img" src="/assets/platforms/steam.svg?v=3" width="28" height="28" alt="" decoding="async" /></span>
                        <span class="auth-platform-btn__main">Steam</span>
                        <span class="auth-platform-btn__sub">Browser</span>
                    </button>
                    <button type="button" class="auth-platform-btn auth-platform-btn--epic" data-provider="epic" title="Epic Games">
                        <span class="auth-platform-btn__ico"><img class="auth-platform-btn__ico-img" src="/assets/platforms/epicgames.svg?v=3" width="28" height="28" alt="" decoding="async" /></span>
                        <span class="auth-platform-btn__main">Epic</span>
                        <span class="auth-platform-btn__sub">Games</span>
                    </button>
                    <button type="button" class="auth-platform-btn auth-platform-btn--xbox" data-provider="xbox" title="Xbox / Microsoft">
                        <span class="auth-platform-btn__ico"><img class="auth-platform-btn__ico-img" src="/assets/platforms/xbox.svg?v=3" width="28" height="28" alt="" decoding="async" /></span>
                        <span class="auth-platform-btn__main">Xbox</span>
                        <span class="auth-platform-btn__sub">Microsoft</span>
                    </button>
                    <button type="button" class="auth-platform-btn auth-platform-btn--ps" data-provider="playstation" title="PlayStation">
                        <span class="auth-platform-btn__ico"><img class="auth-platform-btn__ico-img" src="/assets/platforms/playstation.svg?v=3" width="28" height="28" alt="" decoding="async" /></span>
                        <span class="auth-platform-btn__main">PlayStation</span>
                        <span class="auth-platform-btn__sub">PSN</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
                <p class="token-card__oauth-hint">Choose a platform — a dialog opens with a sign-in link. After login, paste the full redirect URL from your browser (even if the page shows an error).</p>
                <div id="tokenOauthHelp" class="token-oauth-help hidden">
                    <p class="token-oauth-help__title">⚠ Microsoft blocked the login</p>
                    <p class="token-oauth-help__body">Microsoft sometimes blocks automated sign-ins. Try one of these:</p>
                    <ol class="token-oauth-help__steps">
                        <li>Switch to a different browser in <strong>Settings → Browser</strong></li>
                        <li>Sign in to <a href="https://login.live.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">login.live.com</a> in your browser first, then press GET TOKEN again</li>
                        <li>Save a token under <strong>Profiles</strong>, or paste a token in the field below</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
                <label class="token-field">
                    <span class="token-field__label">Access token</span>
                    <div class="token-field__box">
                        <span class="token-field__icon token-field__icon--green" aria-hidden="true">◆</span>
                        <input type="password" id="tokenInput" class="token-field__input" placeholder="Paste token here…" autocomplete="off" spellcheck="false">
                        <button type="button" id="tokenInputEye" class="st-token-eye st-token-eye--overlay" aria-label="Show / hide token" tabindex="-1">
                            <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="16" height="16"><path d="M1 10s3.5-6 9-6 9 6 9 6-3.5 6-9 6-9-6-9-6z"/><circle cx="10" cy="10" r="2.5"/></svg>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </label>
                <button type="button" id="tokenSaveBtn" class="token-card__submit">
                    <span>Continue</span>
                    <span class="token-card__submit-shine" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                </button>
                <div id="tokenError" class="token-card__error" role="alert"></div>
                <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:12px;margin-top:16px;flex-wrap:wrap">
                    <button type="button" id="tokenSkipBtn" class="token-skip-btn" title="Enter without a game token — inventory won't load until you add one in Settings">
                        Skip for now
                        <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
                    </button>
                </div>
                <p class="token-card__legal">© <span id="tokenYear"></span> DEMAN.SOTRE — All rights reserved</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="app-container">
        <header class="header">
            <div class="logo">
                <img class="logo__cls logo__img" src="/assets/deman.png?v=9" width="56" height="56" alt="DEMAN.SOTRE" decoding="async" />
                <div class="logo__text">
                    <h1 id="appTitle">DEMAN.SOTRE</h1>
                    <span class="logo__slogan--sig">V9</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="header__right">
                <div id="statusDot" class="status-dot" title="API status">
                    <span class="status-dot__pulse" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span id="statusDotLabel">Server Optimized</span>
                </div>
                <div id="headerLicenseCountdown" class="header-license-countdown" style="display:none" title="License expiry remaining">
                    <span aria-hidden="true">◇</span><span id="headerLicenseTime">--</span>
                </div>
                <div id="headerSessionTimer" class="header-session-timer" style="display:none" title="Session active time">
                    <svg class="header-timer-icon" aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg><span id="sessionTimerVal">0:00</span>
                </div>
                <div class="header-stats" id="stats" role="status">
                    <span class="stats-pill__inner"><span class="stats-pill__seg">Loading…</span></span>
                </div>
                <button type="button" id="howToUseBtn" class="btn btn-how-to-use">
                    <span class="btn-how-to-use__icon" aria-hidden="true">?</span> HOW TO USE
                </button>
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="portal">
            <aside class="sidebar" aria-label="Navigation">
                <div class="sidebar__brand">
                    <div class="sidebar__brand-title">DEMAN.SOTRE</div>
                    <div class="sidebar__brand-sub dev-by-deman">dev by DEMAN</div>
                </div>
                <nav class="sidebar__nav">
                    <button type="button" class="nav-item is-active" data-page="inventory">
                        <span class="nav-item__ico" aria-hidden="true">▦</span>
                        <span class="nav-item__txt">INVENTORY</span>
                    </button>
                    <button type="button" class="nav-item" data-page="settings">
                        <span class="nav-item__ico" aria-hidden="true">⚙</span>
                        <span class="nav-item__txt">SETTINGS</span>
                    </button>
                    <button type="button" class="nav-item nav-item--profiles" data-page="profiles">
                        <span class="nav-item__ico" aria-hidden="true">
                            <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
                        </span>
                        <span class="nav-item__txt">PROFILES</span>
                    </button>
                </nav>
                <div class="sidebar__tips" aria-label="Quick tips">
                    <div class="sidebar__tips-item"><span class="sidebar__tips-arrow" aria-hidden="true">›</span><span>Equip an augment to use the <strong>Backpack</strong> filter</span></div>
                    <div class="sidebar__tips-item"><span class="sidebar__tips-arrow" aria-hidden="true">›</span><span>Press <strong>Dupe Backpack</strong> once you see the loading wheel</span></div>
                    <div class="sidebar__tips-item"><span class="sidebar__tips-arrow" aria-hidden="true">›</span><span>Press <strong>Stop</strong> once you exit the game</span></div>
                    <div class="sidebar__tips-item"><span class="sidebar__tips-arrow" aria-hidden="true">›</span><span>You must <strong>close in-game inventory</strong> to see changes on the website</span></div>
                    <div class="sidebar__tips-item"><span class="sidebar__tips-arrow" aria-hidden="true">›</span><span>You can leave the game using <strong>hatch, extract, or surrender</strong></span></div>
                    <div class="sidebar__tips-item"><span class="sidebar__tips-arrow" aria-hidden="true">›</span><span>Select weapons &amp; press <strong>Refresh IDs</strong> to repair them</span></div>
                    <div class="sidebar__tips-item"><span class="sidebar__tips-arrow" aria-hidden="true">›</span><span>The augment you equip is <strong>automatically duped</strong></span></div>
                </div>

                <div class="sidebar__footer">
                    <div id="sidebarAccount" class="sidebar__account" style="display:none">
                        <span class="sidebar__account-ico" aria-hidden="true">👤</span>
                        <span id="sidebarAccountName" class="sidebar__account-name"></span>
                        <span id="sidebarAccountLevel" class="sidebar__account-level" style="display:none"></span>
                    </div>

                    <!-- License key display (hidden; stats card replaces on desktop) -->
                    <div id="sidebarLicenseBlock" class="sidebar__license-block" style="display:none">
                        <div class="sidebar__license-label">
                            <span class="sidebar__license-ico" aria-hidden="true">◇</span>
                            License Key
                        </div>
                        <div class="sidebar__license-key" id="sidebarLicenseKey">—</div>
                        <button type="button" class="sidebar__license-revoke" id="sidebarRevokeBtn" title="Remove license and sign out">
                            Sign out
                        </button>
                    </div>

                    <div class="sidebar__auth-block">
                        <div class="sidebar__auth-label">Get token</div>
                        <div class="auth-platform-strip" id="sidebarAuthPlatformGrid" role="group" aria-label="Login platform">
                            <button type="button" class="auth-platform-chip" data-provider="steam" title="Steam"><img class="auth-platform-chip__ico" src="/assets/platforms/steam.svg?v=3" width="18" height="18" alt="" /></button>
                            <button type="button" class="auth-platform-chip" data-provider="epic" title="Epic"><img class="auth-platform-chip__ico" src="/assets/platforms/epicgames.svg?v=3" width="18" height="18" alt="" /></button>
                            <button type="button" class="auth-platform-chip" data-provider="xbox" title="Xbox"><img class="auth-platform-chip__ico" src="/assets/platforms/xbox.svg?v=3" width="18" height="18" alt="" /></button>
                            <button type="button" class="auth-platform-chip" data-provider="playstation" title="PlayStation"><img class="auth-platform-chip__ico" src="/assets/platforms/playstation.svg?v=3" width="18" height="18" alt="" /></button>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Current token reveal -->
                    <div id="sidebarTokenReveal" class="sidebar__token-reveal" style="display:none">
                        <div class="sidebar__token-reveal__label">
                            <svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
                            Current Token
                        </div>
                        <div class="sidebar__token-reveal__row">
                            <input type="password" id="sidebarTokenVal" class="sidebar__token-reveal__inp" value="" readonly placeholder="No active token" autocomplete="off" spellcheck="false">
                            <button type="button" id="sidebarTokenEye" class="sidebar__token-reveal__btn" title="Show / hide token">
                                <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg>
                            </button>
                            <button type="button" id="sidebarTokenCopy" class="sidebar__token-reveal__btn sidebar__token-reveal__btn--copy" title="Copy token">
                                <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="9" y="9" width="13" height="13" rx="2"/><path d="M5 15H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h9a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1"/></svg>
                            </button>
                            <button type="button" id="sidebarTokenLogout" class="sidebar__token-reveal__btn" title="Logout token">
                                <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 21H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h4"/><polyline points="16 17 21 12 16 7"/><line x1="21" y1="12" x2="9" y2="12"/></svg>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- License & Session stats card (desktop) -->
                    <div id="sidebarStatsCard" class="sidebar__stats-card">
                        <div class="sidebar__stats-card__title">
                            <svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
                            License &amp; Session
                        </div>
                        <div class="sidebar__stats-card__row">
                            <div class="sidebar__stats-card__item">
                                <svg class="sidebar__stats-card__ico" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
                                <span class="sidebar__stats-card__label">License</span>
                                <span class="sidebar__stats-card__val sidebar__stats-card__val--lic" id="sidebarLicenseTime">--</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="sidebar__stats-divider"></div>
                            <div class="sidebar__stats-card__item">
                                <svg class="sidebar__stats-card__ico" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
                                <span class="sidebar__stats-card__label">Session</span>
                                <span class="sidebar__stats-card__val" id="sidebarSessionTime">0:00</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </aside>

            <main class="main" aria-label="Content">
                <div class="page-topbar">
                    <div class="page-topbar__titles">
                        <div class="page-topbar__kicker" id="topbarKicker">Inventory</div>
                        <div class="page-topbar__sub" id="topbarSub"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="page-topbar__actions">
                        <div class="cr-balance" id="crBalance" style="display:none">
                            <span class="cr-balance__label">Balance</span>
                            <span class="cr-balance__val" id="crBalanceVal">—</span>
                            <span class="cr-balance__unit">CR</span>
                        </div>
                        <button id="refreshBtn" type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-i18n-refresh-title title="Reload list from server only — instance IDs are unchanged. Use Refresh ID on an item to change an ID.">
                            <span class="btn-icon">↻</span> <span data-i18n-refresh-label>Refresh</span>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <section class="page is-active" id="page-inventory" data-page="inventory">
                    <div class="filters">
                        <div class="filters__row">
                            <div class="filters__group filters__group--grow">
                                <label class="filters__label">Filter</label>
                                <div class="search-box search-box--wide">
                                    <span class="search-icon">⌕</span>
                                    <input type="text" id="searchInput" data-i18n-search-ph placeholder="Filter items…">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="filters__group">
                                <label class="filters__label">Sort</label>
                                <select id="sortBy" class="filters__select">
                                    <option value="name">Name</option>
                                    <option value="amount">Amount</option>
                                    <option value="date">Date</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                            <div class="filters__group filters__group--toggle">
                                <label class="toggle">
                                    <input type="checkbox" id="selectVisibleToggle">
                                    <span class="toggle__track" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                    <span class="toggle__txt">SELECT VISIBLE</span>
                                </label>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="filters__row filters__row--second">
                            <div class="container-filter-group" style="display:flex;gap:4px;align-items:center;">
                                <button type="button" id="containerFilterAll" class="btn btn-secondary active" title="Show all items (stash + backpack)">All Items</button>
                                <button type="button" id="containerFilterStash" class="btn btn-secondary" title="Show only stash items">🏠 Stash</button>
                                <button type="button" id="containerFilterBackpack" class="btn btn-secondary" title="Show only backpack (in-match) items">🎒 Backpack</button>
                            </div>
                            <button type="button" id="refreshedOnlyBtn" class="btn btn-secondary" aria-pressed="false" data-i18n-refreshed-title title="Show only items that have the refreshed badge (Refresh ID this session).">
                                <span data-i18n-refreshed-label>✨ Refreshed only</span>
                            </button>
                            <button type="button" id="clearBadgesBtn" class="btn btn-secondary" title="Remove refreshed badges from UI (does not revert IDs)" style="display:none">
                                Clear badges
                            </button>
                            <button type="button" id="clearSelectionBtn" class="btn btn-secondary" title="Clear selection">
                                Clear Selection (<span id="selectionCount">0</span>)
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div id="loading" class="loading" style="display: none;">
                        <div class="cls-progress-wrap">
                            <div class="cls-progress-bar-track">
                                <div class="cls-progress-bar-fill"></div>
                            </div>
                            <p class="cls-progress-txt" data-i18n-loading-inv>Loading inventory…</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div id="inventoryGrid" class="inv-grid" aria-live="polite"></div>
                    <div id="errorMessage" class="error-message" style="display: none;"></div>

                    <div class="bulk-actions" id="bulkActions" style="display:none">
                        <div class="bulk-actions__left">
                            <span class="bulk-actions__count"><span id="bulkCount">0</span> selected</span>
                            <button type="button" class="bulk-actions__btn bulk-actions__btn--ghost" id="bulkDeselectBtn">DESELECT</button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bulk-actions__right">
                            <button type="button" class="bulk-actions__btn bulk-actions__btn--ghost" id="bulkRefreshIdsBtn" title="Can also repair weapons">REFRESH IDs</button>
                            <button type="button" class="bulk-actions__btn bulk-actions__btn--primary" id="bulkSafePocketBtn">✨ DUPE BACKPACK</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section class="page" id="page-profiles" data-page="profiles">
                    <div class="settings-layout">
                        <div class="settings-section">
                            <div class="settings-section__title">Account Profiles</div>
                            <div class="settings-row profile-save-row">
                                <div class="profile-save-row__header">
                                    <span class="settings-row__label">Save current account</span>
                                    <span class="settings-row__desc">Name and save your active session for quick switching.</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="profile-save-row__inputs">
                                    <input type="text" id="profileNameInputP" class="filters__select profile-name-inp" placeholder="Profile name…">
                                    <button type="button" id="saveProfileBtnP" class="btn btn-secondary profile-save-btn">
                                        <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M19 21H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11l5 5v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z"/><polyline points="17 21 17 13 7 13 7 21"/><polyline points="7 3 7 8 15 8"/></svg>
                                        Save
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="settings-row profile-save-row">
                                <div class="profile-save-row__header">
                                    <span class="settings-row__label">Add account manually</span>
                                    <span class="settings-row__desc">Enter a token directly to save it as a named profile. Profiles are stored in your browser's local storage.</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="profile-save-row__inputs">
                                    <input type="text" id="manualProfileNameInputP" class="filters__select profile-name-inp" placeholder="Profile name…">
                                    <input type="text" id="manualTokenInputP" class="filters__select profile-token-inp" placeholder="Paste token…">
                                    <button type="button" id="addManualProfileBtnP" class="btn btn-secondary profile-save-btn">
                                        <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
                                        Add
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="settings-row" style="cursor:default;flex-direction:column;align-items:stretch;gap:8px">
                                <span class="settings-row__label">Saved profiles</span>
                                <span class="settings-row__desc" style="margin-bottom:4px">Profiles are saved in your browser. Each user sees their own profiles on this device.</span>
                                <div id="profilesListP" class="profiles-list">
                                    <div style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.8rem;padding:4px 0">No profiles saved yet.</div>
                                </div>
                                <div id="profileStatusP" class="profile-status"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section class="page" id="page-settings" data-page="settings">
                    <div class="settings-layout">
                        <div class="settings-section">
                            <div class="settings-section__title">Display</div>
                            <label class="settings-row">
                                <span class="settings-row__label">Show unindexed assets</span>
                                <span class="settings-row__desc">Show items that have no known name or icon in the local database.</span>
                                <label class="toggle toggle--compact">
                                    <input type="checkbox" id="settingShowUnindexed">
                                    <span class="toggle__track" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                </label>
                            </label>
                            <label class="settings-row">
                                <span class="settings-row__label">Card size</span>
                                <span class="settings-row__desc">Choose how large the inventory cards appear.</span>
                                <select id="settingCardSize" class="filters__select">
                                    <option value="normal">Normal</option>
                                    <option value="compact">Compact</option>
                                    <option value="large">Large</option>
                                </select>
                            </label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="settings-section">
                            <div class="settings-section__title">Behaviour</div>
                            <label class="settings-row">
                                <span class="settings-row__label">Auto-refresh on tab focus</span>
                                <span class="settings-row__desc">Reload inventory automatically when you switch back to this tab.</span>
                                <label class="toggle toggle--compact">
                                    <input type="checkbox" id="settingAutoRefresh">
                                    <span class="toggle__track" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                </label>
                            </label>
                            <label class="settings-row">
                                <span class="settings-row__label">Confirm before bulk actions</span>
                                <span class="settings-row__desc">Show a confirmation dialog before Scrap, Recycle, and Refresh ID bulk operations.</span>
                                <label class="toggle toggle--compact">
                                    <input type="checkbox" id="settingConfirmBulk" checked>
                                    <span class="toggle__track" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                </label>
                            </label>
                            <label class="settings-row">
                                <span class="settings-row__label">Sound notifications</span>
                                <span class="settings-row__desc">Play a subtle chime when a bulk operation (Refresh IDs / Dupe) finishes.</span>
                                <label class="toggle toggle--compact">
                                    <input type="checkbox" id="settingSoundNotif">
                                    <span class="toggle__track" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                </label>
                            </label>
                            <label class="settings-row">
                                <span class="settings-row__label">Haptic feedback</span>
                                <span class="settings-row__desc">Vibrate briefly on button press (supported mobile devices only).</span>
                                <label class="toggle toggle--compact">
                                    <input type="checkbox" id="settingHaptic" checked>
                                    <span class="toggle__track" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                                </label>
                            </label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="settings-section">
                            <div class="settings-section__title">Data</div>
                            <div class="settings-row">
                                <span class="settings-row__label">Find ID</span>
                                <span class="settings-row__desc">
                                    <strong>Step 1:</strong> Click <em>Snapshot</em> to record all current gameAssetIds.<br>
                                    <strong>Step 2:</strong> Remove an item in-game, then refresh inventory.<br>
                                    <strong>Step 3:</strong> Click <em>Find Changed</em> — it will print only the IDs that disappeared or changed amount.
                                    <span id="findIdStatus" style="display:block;margin-top:4px;color:#bc00ff;font-size:0.78rem"></span>
                                </span>
                                <button type="button" id="findIdBtn" class="btn btn-secondary" style="white-space:nowrap">📷 Snapshot</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="settings-section">
                            <div class="settings-section__title">Browser</div>
                            <div class="settings-row">
                                <span class="settings-row__label">Open tool in</span>
                                <span class="settings-row__desc">Choose which browser opens when the tool starts. Only installed browsers are listed.</span>
                                <div class="browser-picker" id="browserPickerWrap">
                                    <select id="settingBrowser" class="filters__select browser-picker__select">
                                        <option value="">Detecting…</option>
                                    </select>
                                    <span id="browserPickerStatus" class="browser-picker__status"></span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="settings-section">
                            <div class="settings-section__title">About</div>
                            <div class="settings-about">
                                <div class="settings-about__name settings-about__name--grad">DEMAN.SOTRE</div>
                                <div class="settings-about__line">Developed by <strong>DEMAN</strong></div>
                                <div class="settings-about__line" id="settingServerInfo">Server: localhost</div>
                                <div class="settings-about__line"><a href="https://discord.gg/i9p" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="settings-about__link">Discord — DEMAN.SOTRE</a></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </main>
        </div>

        <footer class="site-footer">
            <span class="site-footer__slashes" aria-hidden="true">/////</span>
            <span class="site-footer__line"></span>
            <div class="site-footer__row">
                <img class="site-footer__logo" src="/assets/deman.png?v=9" width="72" height="72" alt="" decoding="async" />
                <p class="site-footer__text">© <span id="footerYear"></span> <strong>DEMAN.SOTRE</strong> — <span class="dev-by-deman">dev by DEMAN</span></p>
            </div>
            <span class="site-footer__slashes site-footer__slashes--bottom" aria-hidden="true">/////</span>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <!-- How To Use Modal -->
    <div id="howToUseModal" class="how-to-modal hidden" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="howToUseTitle">
        <div class="how-to-modal__backdrop"></div>
        <div class="how-to-modal__box">
            <div class="how-to-modal__header">
                <span class="how-to-modal__icon" aria-hidden="true">🖥</span>
                <h2 class="how-to-modal__title" id="howToUseTitle">How to Dupe</h2>
                <button type="button" class="how-to-modal__close" id="howToUseClose" aria-label="Close">×</button>
            </div>
            <ol class="how-to-modal__steps">
                <li class="how-to-modal__step"><span>Equip a <strong>Backpack augment</strong> and place the items you want to dupe inside your inventory</span></li>
                <li class="how-to-modal__step"><span>Press the <strong>Backpack</strong> filter button on the website</span></li>
                <li class="how-to-modal__step"><span>Press <strong>Refresh</strong>, then press <strong>Select Visible</strong></span></li>
                <li class="how-to-modal__step"><span>Go back to the game and <strong>start a match</strong></span></li>
                <li class="how-to-modal__step"><span>Once you see the <strong>loading wheel</strong> on the black loading screen, press <strong>Dupe Backpack</strong> on the website</span></li>
                <li class="how-to-modal__step"><span>When you land in the match, <strong>drop the items</strong> to your friend</span></li>
                <li class="how-to-modal__step"><span><strong>Surrender</strong> and return to Speranza</span></li>
                <li class="how-to-modal__step"><span>Press <strong>Stop</strong> on the website after exiting the game</span></li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="oauthPasteOverlay" class="oauth-paste-overlay hidden" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="oauthPasteTitle">
        <div class="oauth-paste-overlay__backdrop" data-oauth-close="1"></div>
        <div class="oauth-paste-overlay__card">
            <h3 id="oauthPasteTitle" class="oauth-paste-overlay__title">Complete sign-in</h3>
            <p class="oauth-paste-overlay__step"><strong>1.</strong> <a id="oauthPasteOpenLink" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Click here to sign in</a></p>
            <p class="oauth-paste-overlay__step"><strong>2.</strong> After signing in your browser may show an error — that&apos;s expected. Copy the <strong>full URL</strong> from the address bar and paste it below.</p>
            <textarea id="oauthPasteUrlInput" class="oauth-paste-overlay__textarea" rows="3" placeholder="http://127.0.0.1:49172?code=..."></textarea>
            <div class="oauth-paste-overlay__actions">
                <button type="button" id="oauthPasteSubmitBtn" class="btn btn-primary">Submit URL</button>
                <button type="button" id="oauthPasteCancelBtn" class="btn btn-secondary">Cancel</button>
            </div>
            <div id="oauthPasteErr" class="oauth-paste-overlay__err" role="alert"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

